column5: I am a part of a group of eight Okies headed north to invade Lake of the Woods this weekend.  We will be staying at Lake of the Woods Lodge in Sabaskong Bay.  In 20 words or less (or more, I don't mind  ) any locations I should not miss, and go-to lures that I must have.  Pretty broad topic, but we only have four days to fish; one of which is with a guide.
Hopefully your first day is with a guide..  Pick his brain, remember what he says and apply those patterns during the rest of your stay.
